<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Iggy Azalea has collaborated with many different artists over her career.</p>

<p>But on Friday, she managed to surprise even her most loyal fans by posing for a photo with teenage superstar JoJo Siwa.</p>

<p>In a photo shared to Twitter, Iggy and R&amp;B singer Tinashe are all smiles as they pose between a grinning JoJo.</p>

<p>All smiles! Iggy Azalea, JoJo Siwa, and Tinashe posed for a photo together inside of JoJo's house this week</p>

<p>The image was taken inside the mansion where the 17-year-old films many of her YouTube and TikTok videos.</p>

<p>Interestingly enough, Iggy and Tinashe weren't the only celebrities in JoJo's house over the last few days.</p>

<p>On Friday, 90 Day Fiancé star Angela Deem also shared a photo of herself inside the young mogul's house.</p>

<p>Strange bedfellows! On Friday, 90 Day Fiancé star Angela Deem also shared a photo of herself inside the young mogul's house</p>

<p>Iggy and Tinashe recently teamed up for a song together, Dance Like Nobody's Watching.</p>

<p>In the music video for the track, the 30-year-old Australian rapper slipped into a baby blue corset top and princess-perfect pink tulle midi-skirt.</p>

<p>As she posed up a storm in a tattoo-inspired shirt with her blonde locks sticking up like feathers on the back of her head, Tinashe coordinated in a lime green fairytale-inspired minidress.</p>

<p>Work it: Iggy and Tinashe recently teamed up for a song together, Dance Like Nobody's Watching</p>

<p>'Dance all night, don't my a** look right?' the Fancy songstress sang, as the video began with a photo shoot of her and Tinashe. 'Can't pass on a chance, raise your hands up like [you're] a superstar.'</p>

<p>As they danced around and whispered in each other's ears, the performers put their sensational figures on full display and were filmed getting ready behind-the-scenes.</p>

<p>The music video is the first that Iggy has released since welcoming her son Onyx earlier this year.</p>

<p>Baby joy: Iggy welcomed her first child, a son named Onyx, earlier this year</p>
